---
const chapterInfo = {
    bookTitle: "天生我材：金",
    chapterNo: "01",
    title: "第一章：淘金客的午夜",
    date: "2026-04-03"
};
---

<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>{chapterInfo.title} | {chapterInfo.bookTitle}</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Serif+SC:wght@300;500;700&family=ZCOOL+XiaoWei&family=Cinzel&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    
    <style>
        :root {
            --bg-color: #0A9C49; /* 延续小说主题绿 */
            --paper-color: #ffffff;
            --text-color: #1a1a1a;
        }

        body { 
            background-color: var(--bg-color); 
            margin: 0; 
            padding: 0;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
        }

        /* 顶部导航：半透明悬浮 */
        .reader-nav {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 20px 40px;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            font-family: 'Cinzel', serif;
            font-size: 11px;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            position: sticky;
            top: 0;
            background: rgba(10, 156, 73, 0.9);
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            z-index: 10;
        }
        .reader-nav a { color: white; text-decoration: none; opacity: 0.7; transition: 0.3s; }
        .reader-nav a:hover { opacity: 1; }

        /* 阅读容器：模仿纸质书页 */
        .paper {
            max-width: 850px;
            width: 90%;
            background-color: var(--paper-color);
            margin: 40px 0 100px;
            padding: 100px 80px;
            box-shadow: 20px 20px 0px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
            border: 2px solid black;
        }

        header { text-align: center; margin-bottom: 80px; }
        .chap-no { font-family: 'Cinzel'; font-size: 14px; opacity: 0.4; display: block; margin-bottom: 10px; }
        h1 { font-family: 'ZCOOL XiaoWei', serif; font-size: 42px; color: black; margin: 0; }

        /* 正文排版：极致的呼吸感 */
        .content {
            font-family: 'Noto Serif SC', serif;
            font-size: 18px;
            line-height: 2.2; /* 增加行高，方便长文阅读 */
            color: var(--text-color);
            text-align: justify;
        }

        .content p { margin-bottom: 2em; text-indent: 2em; }

        /* 章节末尾装饰 */
        .end-mark { 
            text-align: center; 
            margin-top: 100px; 
            opacity: 0.2; 
            font-family: 'Cinzel';
            letter-spacing: 10px;
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .paper { padding: 60px 30px; margin: 20px 0; }
            h1 { font-size: 32px; }
            .content { font-size: 17px; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <nav class="reader-nav">
        <a href="/novel/long-form/golden-boy">← CONTENTS</a>
        <span style="color: white; opacity: 0.5;">{chapterInfo.bookTitle}</span>
        <a href="#">NEXT CHAPTER →</a>
    </nav>

    <main class="paper">
        <header>
            <span class="chap-no">CHAPTER {chapterInfo.chapterNo}</span>
            <h1>{chapterInfo.title}</h1>
        </header>

        <article class="content">
            <p>
                午夜的淘金场是一片死寂的喧嚣。老张坐在那辆破旧的皮卡车顶，嘴里叼着一根没点燃的烟，眼睛直勾勾地盯着远处矿坑里那抹忽隐忽现的微光。
            </p>
            <p>
                “那就是金子？”我站在车旁，声音在空旷的山谷里显得有些单薄。老张没回话，只是重重地拍了拍车顶的铁皮。铁皮发出的闷响，像是某种古老巨兽的低吟。在这个时代，黄金不再仅仅是金属，它是一种传染病，一种让所有人都能在梦里看到颜色的致幻剂。
            </p>
            <p>
                我的手心里全是被冷汗浸湿的沙砾。我知道，只要迈进那个坑口，我就再也不是原来的我了。
            </p>
            </article>

        <div class="end-mark">FIN</div>
    </main>

    <footer style="color: white; opacity: 0.3; font-family: 'Cinzel'; font-size: 10px; padding-bottom: 60px; letter-spacing: 3px;">
        {chapterInfo.date} / RUIBEET FICTION ARCHIVE
    </footer>

</body>
</html>
